The Secretary to the Ogun State Government, Mr. Taiwo Adeoluwa has been involved in a ghastly motor accident. The accident said to have occurred at Kobape area of Abeokuta, the state capital left the person he was travelling with dead. Adeoluwa who was said to have been badly injured has been rushed to the Federal Medical Centre in Abeokuta for urgent attention. The SSG unconfirmed report was allegedly on his way to Abeokuta for a meeting with funds for disbursement for tomorrow’s election Details later… Source: https://www.newdawnngr.com